testcase.name: Check if video progress attributes are changed accordingly with video playback.
Check if video playback can be forwarded and then rewound with the buttons in the control panel.
Check if the navigation arrows function throughout the "Homepage" and that the focus is displayed correctly.
Check if video playback can be paused and then resumed with the buttons in the control panel.
Check if returning to the "Homepage" works with the "Back" button and that the focus has the correct position every time.
Check if the video is accessible from the "Homepage" and that playback starts correctly.
This is a sample test case on a sample app called WatchMe.
